# Python packaging flow
source-finder -> license-finder {style.stroke-dash: 3}
license-finder -> license-checker {style.stroke-dash: 3}
source-finder -> complexity {style.stroke-dash: 3}
source-finder -> bug-finder {style.stroke-dash: 3}
